Package: libksba
Section: libs
Priority: optional
Architecture: ARCH
Depends: libc (>= 1.1.8), ${shlibs:Depends}
Description: provides an API used to simplify the tasks of working with X.509 certificates
 libksba provides API functions used to simplify the tasks of working with 
 X.509 certificates, CMS data and related objects.
 .
 This package provides the shared library libksba.

Package: libksba-dev
Section: libdevel
Priority: optional
Architecture: ARCH
Depends: libksba (= ${binary:Version}), libgpg-error-dev
Description: Development headers and libksba static library
 This package provides libksba.a, and headers required to build applications,
 libraries or plugins using the libksba API.

Package: libksba-doc
Section: doc
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Recommends: info
Depends: libksba-dev (= ${binary:Version})
Description: documentation for libksba
 This package provides info and man pages for libksba.
